document.full_text: the united nations wants to negotiate "humanitarian corridors" to let more aid into libya where fighting in the east of the country has uprooted tens of thousands and hit food supplies, the u.n. said on wednesday.
document.title: u.n. says wants to negotiate libya aid "corridors"
lines_and_colors: the united nations wants to negotiate "humanitarian corridors" to let more aid into libya where fighting in the east of the country has uprooted tens of thousands and hit food supplies, the u.n. said on wednesday.
